<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5738149>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Preserved specimens of Lepadichthys akiko from Palau (A, BPBM 37705, 12.3mm SL; B–D, BPBM, 37695, 14.0mm SL). A, B, lateral view; C, dorsal view; D, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5738149/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5738151>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Pelvic disc structure of Lepadichthys akiko, BPBM 37705, 12.3mm SL. Bar indicates 0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5738151/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5738153>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Head sensory canal pores of Lepadichthys akiko, BPBM 37695, 14.0mm SL. Bar indicates 1.0mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5738153/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5738155>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Underwater photographs of Lepadichthys akiko from Okinawa Island, Japan (A, KPM-NR 73666; B, KPM-NR 176523). Specimens not collected.Photos by Y. Terada." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5738155/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5738159>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Distributional records of Lepadichthys akiko. Stars and circle indicate records based on collected specimens and underwater photographs, respectively. Closed and open symbols indicate type locality and newly recorded localities, respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5738159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5738157>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Preserved specimen of Lepadichthys bolini from Palau (BPBM 9219, 28.1 mm SL). A, lateral view; B, dorsal view; C, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5738157/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

